Do you want to get into AI by working on a cool technical project, but don’t know where to start? Come to SAIG’s Project Info Session! We will have undergraduate leaders in AI present their personal projects and help get you started with an AI project idea. Learn about exciting applications of AI to various fields and dive into your own AI project! Dinner will be served.
